      "post_content": "For the price of [Loyal Retainers](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Loyal Retainers), I'll just bribe the opponent to concede.   \n  \nI think I'll stick to [Pulsemage Advocate](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pulsemage Advocate), [Breath of Life](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Breath of Life), [Dance of the Dead](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name= Dance of the Dead), [Dreams of the Dead](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Dreams of the Dead), [Exhume](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Exhume), [Victimize](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Victimize), [Elvish Piper](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Elvish Piper), [Quicksilver Amulet](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Quicksilver Amulet), [Aethermage's Touch](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Aethermage's Touch) + [Otherworldly Journey](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Otherworldly Journey)/ [Flicker](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Flicker), [Braids, Conjurer Adept](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Braids, Conjurer Adept), et cetera, et cetera, et cetera....",
