      "id": "PopularPost377762",
      "post_content": "A really good legendary angel that isn't busted wide open. She has been outdone by Shoeldred in the intervening years, but the NPH praetors can't be used without feeling like you're cheating. Reya has a nice balance. I wouldn't feel too bad putting her in a reanimator deck. I was in a stalemated game against a friend's angel deck and didn't feel like reading all of the nonsense that was hitting the field. I was killing something every turn, but this little lady made sure it came right back. How I wished I had a Lure... Then that dimestore hussy, Linvala, came to the party and it was all over. 5/5 ",
      "posted_by": "Pongdok",
